<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>A couple of facts:<BR>
<BR>
1) This weapon is real. It is NOT a phoney.<BR>
<BR>
2) EVERYONE's damage cap comes of at level 20. Up till level 20 it is (weapons dmg*2)+1. Why people think that casters never get their damage cap of is simple- they do not often use melee weapons, and their skill cap is around 100 for offence and 1HB. But they can do more than (weapon dmg*2)+1.<BR>
<BR>
3) It drops in Old Sebilis in Kunark, possibly a random drop but as far as I know only drops of the Gatekeeper thingy in the centre of the city. He is quite a rare spawn, and level 57 to boot, so good luck killing him.</font></td></tr></table>
